#. type: Plain text
#: 2020-04-07-newsletter-38.md:341
msgid ""
"Neither Covid nor climate pay attention to borders, the world is a small "
"place, and we're all interconnected. This is the basis of planetary health. "
"**Prevention is better than cure**."
